    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera. This 996.2 features the 3.6L M96/03 flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a precision G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains its factory rigidity, with the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension tuned for surgical turn-in. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic upgrade, and the rear main seal remains bone dry. The paint meter readings are consistent across all panels, and the underside shows no signs of heat-cycling fatigue or fluid seepage. This is a concours-ready example for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
